<template><section>
<h2 id="layout"><a class="header-anchor" href="#layout" aria-hidden="true">¶</a> Layout</h2>
<p>Quickly and easily create layouts with the basic 24-column.</p>
<h3 id="basic-layout"><a class="header-anchor" href="#basic-layout" aria-hidden="true">¶</a> Basic layout</h3>
